---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="フォトジャーナル — 地域おこし協力隊DAO">
  <div class="journal">
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
          <span class="nav-logo-mark">—</span>
          <span class="nav-logo-text">協力隊DAO</span>
          <span class="nav-logo-sub">JOURNAL</span>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#about"><span class="nav-num">01</span>知る</a>
          <a href="#vision"><span class="nav-num">02</span>理念</a>
          <a href="#join"><span class="nav-num">03</span>参加する</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-photo">
        <div class="photo photo-mountain"></div>
        <div class="photo-caption">
          <span class="caption-label">FIG. 01</span>
          <span class="caption-text">北海道・東川町、朝霧の大雪山。協力隊員が暮らす土地のひとつ。</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="hero-vol">VOL. 01 / SPRING 2026</span>
          <span class="hero-dot"></span>
          <span class="hero-issue">地域おこし協力隊DAO</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          土と、<br />
          人と、<br />
          未来をむすぶ。
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-lede">
          北から南まで、四十七都道府県に散らばる協力隊員たち。<br />
          彼らの声と知恵を、ひとつのコミュニティに結い直す試みがある。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-credits">
          <div class="credit-item">
            <span class="credit-label">EDITED BY</span>
            <span class="credit-value">株式会社あるやうむ</span>
          </div>
          <div class="credit-item">
            <span class="credit-label">PUBLISHED</span>
            <span class="credit-value">2026.04</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Marquee strip -->
    <div class="strip">
      <div class="strip-inner">
        <span>FIELD NOTES</span>
        <span class="strip-dot">◆</span>
        <span>COMMUNITY DISPATCH</span>
        <span class="strip-dot">◆</span>
        <span>SINCE 2024</span>
        <span class="strip-dot">◆</span>
        <span>ALL 47 PREFECTURES</span>
        <span class="strip-dot">◆</span>
        <span>DECENTRALIZED</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-num">— 01 —</span>
        <span class="section-kicker">ABOUT</span>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-lead">
          <p class="drop-cap">
            <span class="drop">地</span>域おこし協力隊は、都市から地方へ生活拠点を移し、その土地の未来をともに耕す人々のことだ。いま全国に七千人。しかし彼らの多くは、それぞれの土地で、それぞれの課題と向き合い、ときに孤独のなかで日々を過ごしている。
          </p>
          <p>
            地域おこし協力隊DAOは、そうした隊員たちを、地域の境界を越えてつなぎ直すためのコミュニティだ。分散型自律組織——DAO——の仕組みを借り、知恵と経験を共有財として積み上げていく。株式会社あるやうむが編集の役を担い、Web3の技術が、届きにくかった声に道筋を与える。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-photo">
          <div class="photo photo-field"></div>
          <div class="photo-caption">
            <span class="caption-label">FIG. 02</span>
            <span class="caption-text">長野・伊那谷。春先、田に水が張られる。</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">47</span>
          <span class="stat-unit">都道府県</span>
          <span class="stat-note">隊員が暮らす土地</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">7,000<span class="stat-plus">+</span></span>
          <span class="stat-unit">協力隊員</span>
          <span class="stat-note">現役・OBOGの総数</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">2024</span>
          <span class="stat-unit">設立年</span>
          <span class="stat-note">DAOとしての航海のはじまり</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">∞</span>
          <span class="stat-unit">共創の回数</span>
          <span class="stat-note">越境で生まれる化学反応</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Editorial divider photo -->
    <section class="spread">
      <div class="photo photo-sea"></div>
      <div class="spread-quote">
        <p>「地域の未来は、</p>
        <p>そこに暮らす人の手のなかに。」</p>
        <span class="spread-author">— 協力隊員・寄稿より</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision -->
    <section id="vision" class="vision">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-num">— 02 —</span>
        <span class="section-kicker">PRINCIPLES</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="vision-title">
        一人の火は小さくとも、<br />
        集えば、大地をあたためる。
      </h2>

      <div class="pillars">
        <article class="pillar">
          <div class="photo photo-forest"></div>
          <div class="pillar-body">
            <span class="pillar-num">I.</span>
            <h3>知恵を、土に還す</h3>
            <p>
              各地の隊員が携えてきたノウハウ、失敗、ささやかな発見。ひとつひとつを記録し、次の挑戦者へと受け継ぐ。言葉は土のようにゆっくりと積もり、やがて誰かの足場になる。
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="pillar">
          <div class="photo photo-soil"></div>
          <div class="pillar-body">
            <span class="pillar-num">II.</span>
            <h3>境界を、越えて編む</h3>
            <p>
              青森の林業と高知の漁村に、同じ問いがあることがある。地域の壁を越え、共通のテーマを持つ隊員同士が出会い、越境した協働プロジェクトが生まれる場をつくる。
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="pillar">
          <div class="photo photo-night"></div>
          <div class="pillar-body">
            <span class="pillar-num">III.</span>
            <h3>仕組みを、つづける</h3>
            <p>
              誰か一人に依存しない運営のために、DAOの仕組みを選んだ。透明な意思決定と、参加者が当事者となる設計で、長く続くコミュニティを育てていく。
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Field dispatch -->
    <section class="dispatch">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-num">— 03 —</span>
        <span class="section-kicker">FIELD DISPATCH</span>
      </div>

      <div class="dispatch-grid">
        <article class="dispatch-item">
          <div class="photo photo-field dispatch-photo"></div>
          <span class="dispatch-tag">NOTE / 北海道</span>
          <h4>雪解けのあとで、畑を編集する</h4>
          <p>移住三年目の隊員が、休耕田の再生に取り組む。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="dispatch-item">
          <div class="photo photo-sea dispatch-photo"></div>
          <span class="dispatch-tag">NOTE / 高知</span>
          <h4>漁村のDAO、小さな一歩</h4>
          <p>水揚げのデータを隊員同士で共有する試み。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="dispatch-item">
          <div class="photo photo-forest dispatch-photo"></div>
          <span class="dispatch-tag">NOTE / 岐阜</span>
          <h4>林業の継承と、デジタルの余白</h4>
          <p>山仕事の知恵を、映像と対話で記録する。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="dispatch-item">
          <div class="photo photo-mountain dispatch-photo"></div>
          <span class="dispatch-tag">NOTE / 長野</span>
          <h4>山村から、教育の地平へ</h4>
          <p>小さな村の学校を、越境する学び場に。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section id="join" class="cta">
      <div class="cta-photo">
        <div class="photo photo-night photo-cta"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-body">
        <span class="cta-kicker">— JOIN THE JOURNAL —</span>
        <h2>
          あなたの土地の物語を、<br />
          次の号に、書き加えよう。
        </h2>
        <p class="cta-lede">
          現役隊員、OBOG、地域に関わるすべての人へ。<br />
          対話の場は、すでにひらかれています。
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">
          <span>コミュニティへ参加する</span>
          <span class="cta-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <div class="cta-foot">
          <span>運営 — 株式会社あるやうむ</span>
          <span class="cta-sep">/</span>
          <span>EST. 2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="foot">
      <div class="foot-inner">
        <span>協力隊DAO JOURNAL — VOL.01</span>
        <span>© 2026 ARUYAUMU INC.</span>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← デザイン一覧に戻る</a>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .journal {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #f5f3ee;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Photo placeholders */
  .photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 260px;
    position: relative;
    background: #cfcfcf;
  }
  .photo::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 80%, rgba(0,0,0,0.15), transparent 55%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .photo-mountain { background: linear-gradient(165deg, #bcc9c6 0%, #8ea8a5 40%, #5c7b6d 70%, #2d3d38 100%); }
  .photo-forest   { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #3a4b2e 0%, #4f6238 40%, #2b3720 80%, #1c2416 100%); }
  .photo-field    { background: linear-gradient(175deg, #e6dcb4 0%, #c9b878 35%, #8f9a4e 75%, #586739 100%); }
  .photo-sea      { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d4dde0 0%, #8fa6ac 30%, #4b6d77 65%, #24404a 100%); }
  .photo-night    { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1b2240 0%, #2a2f56 35%, #141632 70%, #0a0b1a 100%); }
  .photo-soil     { background: linear-gradient(170deg, #a37a54 0%, #704a31 45%, #3d2a1b 85%, #1f140c 100%); }

  /* Nav */
  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(245, 243, 238, 0.94);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
  }
  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 18px 48px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .nav-logo-mark {
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .nav-logo-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .nav-logo-sub {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #8a8276;
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 36px;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    transition: color 0.25s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: #8a6a3f; }
  .nav-num {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #8a8276;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 120px 48px 64px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  .hero-photo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .hero-photo .photo {
    min-height: 560px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .photo-caption {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #6b645a;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
  }
  .caption-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .caption-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 0;
  }
  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #6b645a;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
  }
  .hero-vol { font-weight: 600; }
  .hero-dot {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #8a6a3f;
  }
  .hero-issue { font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5.5vw, 4.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 48px 0;
  }
  .hero-lede {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2.1;
    color: #3a3530;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .hero-credits {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
  }
  .credit-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .credit-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #8a8276;
  }
  .credit-value {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Strip */
  .strip {
    border-top: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #f5f3ee;
  }
  .strip-inner {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 14px 48px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .strip-dot { color: #8a6a3f; }

  /* About */
  .about {
    padding: 140px 48px 120px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }
  .section-num {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #8a6a3f;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .section-kicker {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 96px;
  }
  .about-lead p {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #2d2822;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .drop-cap { position: relative; }
  .drop {
    font-size: 3.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    float: left;
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 6px 14px 0 0;
    color: #8a6a3f;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  }

  .about-photo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .about-photo .photo {
    min-height: 420px;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
  }
  .stat {
    padding: 36px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    border-right: 1px solid #d4cfc4;
  }
  .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .stat-plus {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #8a6a3f;
    vertical-align: super;
  }
  .stat-unit {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .stat-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #6b645a;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* Spread */
  .spread {
    position: relative;
    height: 68vh;
    min-height: 460px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .spread .photo {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    min-height: 100%;
  }
  .spread-quote {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color: #f5f3ee;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 32px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .spread-quote p {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.8vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .spread-author {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* Vision */
  .vision {
    padding: 140px 48px 120px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .vision-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.6vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .pillar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .pillar .photo {
    min-height: 320px;
  }
  .pillar-body {
    padding-top: 4px;
    border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding: 16px 0 0;
  }
  .pillar-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: #8a6a3f;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .pillar-body h3 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .pillar-body p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #3a3530;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Dispatch */
  .dispatch {
    padding: 40px 48px 140px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .dispatch-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
  }
  .dispatch-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .dispatch-photo {
    min-height: 220px !important;
  }
  .dispatch-tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #8a6a3f;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .dispatch-item h4 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .dispatch-item p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #6b645a;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 78vh;
